{"tid":2317138,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"作為歌手的《2020 MAMA》頒獎典禮！演員、歌手的待機室大不同，Ment差別待遇引發爭議！","createTime":"2020-12-08T10:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T11:17:50.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"71ebf996da93c5e20dcb6f8c108a9ba655f441e0","tid":2317138,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_8a47b947b7a19142a02a78f3c6066954/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-08/132171-888073.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_8a47b947b7a19142a02a78f3c6066954%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-08%2F132171-888073.jpg&h=d72013e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一年一度的音樂人盛典MAMA（Mnet Asian Music Awards），無論是歌手、粉絲們都非常激動，每年的規模也越來越大。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《2020 MAMA》在6日於韓國舉行，不少演員、歌手都出席頒獎典禮，並帶來了精彩的舞台表演。（完整得獎名單：<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/132135\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F132135&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3WxdyOQTk4RMct2Rsqyof94c%3D&h=63497a13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/132135</a>）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但...也因為Mnet的差別待遇，在韓網引發熱烈討論。作為頒獎嘉賓的演員們，有獨立的待機室、化妝台、餐飲等，而歌手則是在寒冷的室外待機，工作人員用手機的燈光幫他們補妝。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_8b5d89b0a7309ab45e34fa99d910bc7b/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-08/132171-888056.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_8b5d89b0a7309ab45e34fa99d910bc7b%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-08%2F132171-888056.png&h=452a9773&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_7c6faf2894d896e40f77f75a4d8ca1dd/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-08/132171-888057.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_7c6faf2894d896e40f77f75a4d8ca1dd%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-08%2F132171-888057.png&h=f15b2050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d8b430dd33da7b48f92d26ff9f228be2/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-08/132171-888059.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d8b430dd33da7b48f92d26ff9f228be2%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-08%2F132171-888059.png&h=20adb342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌手們在外面等待頒獎時、領獎時幾乎都戴著口罩，但演員們頒獎時、在休息室裡並沒有口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_8c3ce196a883cde4e54998b47b8e5923/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-08/132171-888060.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_8c3ce196a883cde4e54998b47b8e5923%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-08%2F132171-888060.png&h=8c57ee01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_619cac948bb0717e86a1b6dddcf687a6/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-08/132171-888069.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_619cac948bb0717e86a1b6dddcf687a6%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-08%2F132171-888069.png&h=a96f0805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_8e4678d5bb391422410a6b2aa085a66e/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-08/132171-888067.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_8e4678d5bb391422410a6b2aa085a66e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-08%2F132171-888067.jpg&h=1d5139be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這也讓不少網友表示：「歌手作為主人公的頒獎典禮上受到如此待遇，這像話嗎」、「暈... 差距這麼大」、「演員們爲什麼不戴口罩」、「我愛豆在車裡來回走了好幾次，歌手的頒獎典禮讓他們在車上待機是正常的嗎」、「是啊！所以我們泰民說沒有待機室」、「以防疫為藉口，赤裸裸地分階級，真是讓人噁心」、「歌手和工作人員真的辛苦了」、「太過分了，那天我愛豆肯定夜這樣」、「我都覺得委屈」、「冷死了&hellip;&hellip;爲什麼不給待機室」、「以後不看Mnet節目了」等等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_121c981a4e8ac9cdf0b09f230d9e61a9/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-08/132171-888062.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_121c981a4e8ac9cdf0b09f230d9e61a9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-08%2F132171-888062.jpg&h=41ecfd40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b126b143266ca7bce2a5f3b07bb9a43eb467886","tid":2317138,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:56:15.000Z","msg":"真係痴𠃊線公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec78e5f2bd728b539096edea2ab39c1cf26d15d","tid":2317138,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b126b143266ca7bce2a5f3b07bb9a43eb467886","tid":2317138,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:56:15.000Z","msg":"真係痴𠃊線公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:56:47.000Z","msg":"公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57e0469b235a49ba4f356964632c895411eb410","tid":2317138,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ec78e5f2bd728b539096edea2ab39c1cf26d15d","tid":2317138,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b126b143266ca7bce2a5f3b07bb9a43eb467886","tid":2317138,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:56:15.000Z","msg":"真係痴𠃊線公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:56:47.000Z","msg":"公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},